blockquote><blockquote>其實幾多%similarity先會俾人當係plagiarism?</blockquote><br />\nBelow 20%？</blockquote><br />\n其實冇直接間係<br />\n只係高% 嘅話 會特別被人留意<br />\n<br />\n睇個 tutor or prof 有冇用心改<br />\n因為turnitin 蠢到仆街<br />\n 如果你成個例子都係抄 但佔篇文好少% <br />\n你都係抄<br />\n<br />\n而你落晒 citation 又啱曬格式<br />\n通常都冇事<br />\n<br />\n試過篇paper 45% similarity 都拎A<br />\n仲被個鬼佬prof 點名讚寫得好"},{"pid":"c8c18d68b0d0b022860bf347d079ba453847231b","tid":218853,"uid":64699,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T14:42:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d610bb7dc7e755ede714d840c4abf14af22e055f","tid":218853,"uid":64699,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T14:46:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f3e90ac0bda868bcf18424518b0909596add5a26","tid":218853,"uid":33643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T14:49:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實幾多%similarity先會俾人當係plagiarism?</blockquote><br />\n睇你個科<br />\n冇指定number"},{"pid":"b241c7646bfdc2dcc2d15e24718ec4b8b99b3731","tid":218853,"uid":33643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T14:51:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢啲垃圾tutor真係麻撚煩搞屎棍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n乜撚嘢叫self plagiarism 乜撚嘢自我抄襲 樓主上一篇文唔係自己做?自己做嘅文就係自己嘅財產 鍾意今次用就今次用 下次用就下次 你條題目咁啱同其他course近似吖嘛 屌你老母咁你條essay題目係咪又抄鳩其他professor呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n樓主我撐你</blockquote><br />\non9啦<br />\n唔同科黎咖on9"},{"pid":"9ecdcbc8e93b6eb03fb43732934a85be850ebbe9","tid":218853,"uid":33643,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T14:56:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢啲垃圾tutor真係麻撚煩搞屎棍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n乜撚嘢叫self plagiarism 乜撚嘢自我抄襲 樓主上一篇文唔係自己做?自己做嘅文就係自己嘅財產 鍾意今次用就今次用 下次用就下次 你條題目咁啱同其他course近似吖嘛 屌你老母咁你條essay題目係咪又抄鳩其他professor呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n樓主我撐你</blockquote><br />\non9啦<br />\n唔同科黎咖on9</blockquote><br />\nWhy is it bad? Because it&rsquo;s equivalent to trying to spend the same dollar bill twice by making a photocopy of it. The original is real money. The second one is worthless.<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83d1717d0de7e4a59134ee3ae69a5afbe2e761f1","tid":218853,"uid":64699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T15:06:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"90bc368a0995db3d8aac8e102c7bf5b79a47ca92","tid":218853,"uid":33643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T17:14:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>呢啲垃圾tutor真係麻撚煩搞屎棍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n乜撚嘢叫self plagiarism 乜撚嘢自我抄襲 樓主上一篇文唔係自己做?自己做嘅文就係自己嘅財產 鍾意今次用就今次用 下次用就下次 你條題目咁啱同其他course近似吖嘛 屌你老母咁你條essay題目係咪又抄鳩其他professor呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n樓主我撐你</blockquote><br />\non9啦<br />\n唔同科黎咖on9</blockquote><br />\nWhy is it bad? Because it&rsquo;s equivalent to trying to spend the same dollar bill twice by making a photocopy of it. The original is real money. The second one is worthless.<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n宜家係我自己種咗一舊蕃茄 一啲黎煮蕃茄炒蛋 一啲黎煮肉醬意粉</blockquote><br />\n你係種左舊蕃茄<br />\n一D加鹽食<br />\n一D加胡椒食"},{"pid":"93b8b9f632c21ab5571378092428154ea5d7d0ad","tid":218853,"uid":26003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T18:20:00.000Z","msg":"其實肯自己做根本就唔洗理咩plagiarism<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31ea43703cc1e9093ae4fa7dfcc3604ff03a3c9e","tid":218853,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T18:24:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>呢啲垃圾tutor真係麻撚煩搞屎棍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n乜撚嘢叫self plagiarism 乜撚嘢自我抄襲 樓主上一篇文唔係自己做?